  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is the assessment B-cell immune responses in HIV-infected individuals.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Groups of patients with different immune competencies will be examined. The impact of HIV
      infection on immune response will be assessed.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
